img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148ba1048168a2ef61ccd31fd2d33d0746ae6cbf","tid":1242247,"uid":50889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:11:16.000Z","msg":"講滿意果啲人究竟係咩心態 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb8b1193b3b8a6e3bf2495e06f3f9714ba2ef7f","tid":1242247,"uid":91897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:13:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">該項於6月初、在最近兩次百萬人大遊行示威前進行</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d1e4fba5f6730bd5f75356b3eee80f23e9c006","tid":1242247,"uid":263377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"低處未算低，再咁搞落去啲差佬行街分分鐘會俾人吐口水"}]}